    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a buyer who prioritizes mechanical integrity and a well-cared-for interior. The exterior maintains a brilliant finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the door handle consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats are soft and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts crisply, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With plenty of tread remaining on the tires and a recently serviced cooling system, this car is prepared for many more miles of dependable service. It is a solid, honest example of a vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
